#a) how to upload
# mkdir <name of repo>
# cd <name of repo>
# git init
# touch README
# git commit -m 'first commit'
# git remote add origin git@github.com:tornow/backup_scripts.git
# git push origin master


b) how to upload again
   1. Edit file(s)
   2. git commit -a
   3. git push origin master

